  background-color: orange;
  height: 96px;
  padding: 0px;
  width: 96px;
  }
  ]]></style>

 </head>

 <body>

  <p>Test passes if a filled orange square is vertically centered inside a bigger filled blue square.</p>

  <table>
    <tr><td></td></tr>  
  </table>

